values: haha people still write in these things? hahaaaaaaaa

So last night was the Starting Line and The Almost show Alex & I drove like 3 hours to Grand Rapids it was totally worth it. The show was amaaaaazing. We ended up talking to the merch guy and he let us stay after everyone else got kicked out so we could meet Aaron. haha it was so sweet. We talked to them for a little while. They were all so nice We got our ticket signed by aaron and the drummer and we got TSL picks! haha it was seriously the best night. =-]
